text: Ambiyak hebeltô Nabiih maxiqtaay matakka xannabak tu-garqaah isi kataysis ganam, xannabâ maaluk tu-ganoh bee num, Qhiyaamah Ayró usuk ganoh Beeh yanim Quukak baaha Sinam foocal edde wacarriyamkeh, tohuk lakal ummaan nafsi Abba heemil galto dudda-luk kaah tantacawwime usun edde Andullume kalah
